<Page name="Example" icon="layout-grid">
  <Query id="example" path="/example">
    <Hero title="XML component showcase" subtitle="A guided example page for the built-in XML runtime." icon="layout-grid" action="Open dialog">
      <DialogContent>
        <DialogHeader>
          <DialogTitle>XML showcase dialog</DialogTitle>
          <DialogDescription>Quick reference for the page layout and available sections.</DialogDescription>
        </DialogHeader>
        <Stack gap="12">
          <p>The example page highlights the hero, menu, HTML, table, and layout sections.</p>
          <Button variant="default">Close</Button>
        </Stack>
      </DialogContent>
    </Hero>

    <Menu>
      <MenuSection title="HTML" icon="code">
        <MenuSubSection title="Element showcase" root="true">
          <h1>Heading one</h1>
          <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Sed non risus. Suspendisse lectus tortor, dignissim sit amet, adipiscing nec, ultricies sed, dolor.</p>
          <h2>Heading two</h2>
          <p>Cras elementum ultrices diam. Maecenas ligula massa, varius a, semper congue, euismod non, mi. Proin porttitor, orci nec nonummy molestie.</p>
          <h3>Heading three</h3>
          <p>Fusce posuere, magna sed pulvinar ultricies, purus lectus malesuada libero, sit amet commodo magna eros quis urna.</p>
          <h4>Heading four</h4>
          <p>Paragraph content explains how standard HTML elements render in XML pages.</p>
          <blockquote>Blockquote content highlights longer quoted text.</blockquote>
          <ul>
            <li>Unordered list item one</li>
            <li>Unordered list item two</li>
          </ul>
        </MenuSubSection>
      </MenuSection>

      <MenuSection title="Table" icon="table">
        <MenuSubSection title="Data showcase" root="true">
          <Table data='[{"item":"XML showcase page","quantity":1,"unitPrice":"$120.00","total":"$120.00"},{"item":"Layout composition","quantity":2,"unitPrice":"$45.00","total":"$90.00"},{"item":"Documentation polish","quantity":1,"unitPrice":"$80.00","total":"$80.00"}]'>
            <TableHeader>
              <TableRow>
                <TableHead>Item</TableHead>
                <TableHead>Quantity</TableHead>
                <TableHead>Unit price</TableHead>
                <TableHead>Total</TableHead>
              </TableRow>
            </TableHeader>
            <TableBody>
              <TableRow>
                <TableCell>{item}</TableCell>
                <TableCell>{quantity}</TableCell>
                <TableCell>{unitPrice}</TableCell>
                <TableCell>{total}</TableCell>
              </TableRow>
            </TableBody>
          </Table>
        </MenuSubSection>
      </MenuSection>

      <MenuSection title="Form" icon="file-text">
        <MenuSubSection title="Form controls" root="true">
          <p>This section showcases the inputs commonly used to build forms in XML pages.</p>
          <Stack gap="12">
            <Input kind="text" label="Full name" placeholder="Ada Lovelace" />
            <Input kind="email" label="Email address" placeholder="ada@example.com" />
            <Textarea label="Notes" placeholder="Add a short note" />
            <Checkbox label="Subscribe to updates" checked="true" />
            <Switch label="Enable notifications" active="true" />
            <Button variant="default">Submit form</Button>
          </Stack>
        </MenuSubSection>
      </MenuSection>

      <MenuSection title="Cards" icon="layers-3">
        <MenuSubSection title="GPU models" root="true">
          <p>This section combines search and cards to present a compact catalog of GPU models.</p>
          <Input kind="text" label="Search GPUs" placeholder="Search by model name" />
          <Columns>
            <Column key="col-1" label="Column 1" content="" align="left">
              <Card>
                <CardHeader>
                  <CardTitle>NVIDIA RTX 4090</CardTitle>
                  <CardDescription>Flagship card for high-end rendering and AI workloads.</CardDescription>
                </CardHeader>
                <CardContent>
                  <p>24 GB GDDR6X, best suited for demanding workstation tasks.</p>
                </CardContent>
              </Card>
              <Card>
                <CardHeader>
                  <CardTitle>NVIDIA RTX 4070 Ti</CardTitle>
                  <CardDescription>Efficient upper-midrange option for creators.</CardDescription>
                </CardHeader>
                <CardContent>
                  <p>12 GB GDDR6X, good fit for balanced performance targets.</p>
                </CardContent>
              </Card>
            </Column>
            <Column key="col-2" label="Column 2" content="" align="left">
              <Card>
                <CardHeader>
                  <CardTitle>NVIDIA RTX 4080</CardTitle>
                  <CardDescription>Strong performance for premium creative workflows.</CardDescription>
                </CardHeader>
                <CardContent>
                  <p>16 GB GDDR6X, balanced for gaming and content creation.</p>
                </CardContent>
              </Card>
              <Card>
                <CardHeader>
                  <CardTitle>AMD Radeon RX 7800 XT</CardTitle>
                  <CardDescription>Mainstream card for high-refresh 1440p.</CardDescription>
                </CardHeader>
                <CardContent>
                  <p>16 GB GDDR6, practical value-oriented GPU choice.</p>
                </CardContent>
              </Card>
            </Column>
            <Column key="col-3" label="Column 3" content="" align="left">
              <Card>
                <CardHeader>
                  <CardTitle>AMD Radeon RX 7900 XTX</CardTitle>
                  <CardDescription>High-memory GPU for broad 4K and compute usage.</CardDescription>
                </CardHeader>
                <CardContent>
                  <p>24 GB GDDR6, competitive in rasterized workloads.</p>
                </CardContent>
              </Card>
              <Card>
                <CardHeader>
                  <CardTitle>NVIDIA RTX 4060</CardTitle>
                  <CardDescription>Entry-level card with modern encoder support.</CardDescription>
                </CardHeader>
                <CardContent>
                  <p>8 GB GDDR6, compact option for smaller builds.</p>
                </CardContent>
              </Card>
            </Column>
          </Columns>
        </MenuSubSection>
      </MenuSection>

      <MenuSection title="Layout" icon="columns-2">
        <MenuSubSection title="Composition" root="true">
          <Columns>
            <Column key="left" label="Left" content="Sectioned content" align="left" />
            <Column key="right" label="Right" content="Structured presentation" align="left" />
          </Columns>
        </MenuSubSection>
      </MenuSection>
    </Menu>
  </Query>
</Page>
